>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223762600843/004.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6b322785-f8b0-4624-a3bb-59b8ee196a37\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-671d7c9c-5a57-4fc5-9fee-8fd3af23b63c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9a9b0491-81fc-4e00-9cea-02e34c79f2bd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제 패키지도 소량으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e8a994b8-0ecc-43cb-bcda-e4b895a460f3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b5f03b68-582b-4b9e-881e-abb1eb52756d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플을 만들고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-011f52bf-f85c-4b0f-9340-ab157fff5946\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-668f8ea6-4aca-44a3-ac61-02ef1ec174a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주문하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-add8b7f2-e457-4f56-9cd4-06b1301c9aaa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bd8fa582-2ce3-46f1-b60e-9f24daf2c984\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이렇게 작업해야 안전합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d6ea4fc4-919d-4750-adc5-d301670c143f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223762600843/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-2450da87-fe08-4212-a4ea-1931c4f68b8a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1677b294-67a3-45bf-89d4-cc7ace378a75\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7e291c36-7920-49bf-b349-6b6354b0482e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">샘플을 만들어야 하는 이유</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-225780e8-6998-41a5-b2a1-7735e172fbe2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7f517e74-9c74-4230-87e9-8d98ca812cf1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8f215d5c-871d-425d-a1ee-407e200d2f78\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지는 반드시 샘플을 만들고 본 작업을 하시기를 추천드립니다. 샘플을 만드는데 비용도 많이 들고 여러 가지 납기 등을 고려해야 할 사항이 많지만 그럼에도 불구하고 샘플 작업은 이제 필수가 되었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98e98ea2-88c4-4c2d-a68b-bec0e6cfeedd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ddd3bc61-4c13-4465-b752-8a0f08f457aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8f6d647c-efed-4db7-977b-89453c5ecdb0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-029bdf82-353f-4bdc-9721-275af64b42c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니이 샘플을 추천드리는 이유는 다음과 같습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-18b11ffd-18fb-4c8e-8e2f-97b01c0b5881\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ea6c467-f17b-4dce-8187-d90119733caf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-500304f7-c169-4653-ae11-0f49e5c14395\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7bbb0377-6a8f-4a1a-9320-298c16ddaed0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하나, 제품을 실제 넣어보면 헐겁거나 빡빡해 삽입이 어려운 경우가 발생합니다. 이런 경우는 정말로 난감합니다. 반드시 샘플을 제작하여 확인하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1c436bd9-e91d-4366-8ea0-f09141044ce7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f6baef64-7197-410a-b242-123aaac6bb56\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-639da17e-0d7d-4157-9b58-53a728ebf7d7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bc5c2681-107f-48c8-9c4b-2ee47ec5e1d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">둘, 제품의 방향과 위아래를 혼동하는 경우도 종종 발생합니다. 뚜껑의 방향과 앞면, 뒷면은 꼼꼼히 따져 작업하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ec76bc5-7a14-4ba9-b4ac-fcaf2e9a9572\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03dc7a6f-fc03-49c1-ae6a-5338e70b1b4c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-128ecee5-e189-4cb6-8661-6551327954b6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05dbf59b-6a7e-44a9-9afe-b050ff692a7a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">셋, 실제 샘플을 받아보면 수정하거나 보강해야 하는 부분이 보입니다. 예를 들어 후공정으로 조금 더 이쁘게 만들 걸 하는 후회는 샘플을 작업하고서 느끼게 됩니다. 이런 이유로 반드시 샘플 작업을 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-059c4f58-a9cb-41e7-b164-1afcba4813f6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2fa8d279-a1b3-4439-944f-0be2a1e80512\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dee01196-6430-4acf-8959-c151fa736d2f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9e78bc0c-775e-458a-a592-93c338edb551\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>이제 (주)파파스컴퍼니이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4b1