-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d107af43-6ee0-4bce-a170-2fe60c8271a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">양해하여 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-369f4231-a64a-4e1c-a720-0bfc970df9d7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-71264a76-7a95-4b7c-887c-46e595534b2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">접착은 양면테이프가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-80f2b8d9-560c-4c4f-9355-f8cbe5150b7e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4600b0ea-9da4-4713-8c0b-0c6219fff278\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-a54cf07c-63a2-4f3f-9670-14a95345dbb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-898d4b33-ee13-4a4e-b16a-87797820ab51\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223762600843/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6ebd8178-c294-4fb7-a408-3b6dd1744252\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0bce81d0-627b-426f-96ec-bdb4e4145a6b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>납기에 대한 조건</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-657df1ad-f8c5-4e74-8859-417a7ed1cc34\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09223316-6b19-448d-a5ef-abb9dc893cc6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-adddd191-8faf-4ae3-b432-11607d44ee69\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-203cba83-01cb-4e58-a432-a805eedf906c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">커팅은 사이즈에 영향을 받습니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3cd0aa24-9c33-4147-907f-75de83471018\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">A3가 넘어가면 칼선을 후면에 양면인쇄하여 손커팅이 훨씬 저렴하거나 납기를 맞출 수 있습니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-95e2d2cc-ec40-4428-b1ad-210785199227\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (주)파파스컴퍼니은 A3 넘어가는 사이즈의 경우 커팅 없이 당일 출고가 가능합니다. 급하신 고객님은 인쇄와 코팅만을 접수하시기를 추천드립니다. 또는 일정 비용을 받고 저희가 커팅 하여 출고해 드립니다. 다만 납기는 하루 더 소요될 수 있으니 참고하시기 바랍니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 고객의 시간을 가장 중요하게 생각합니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f644d4c4-5342-4688-8bcf-63f032982c45\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">최선을 다하는 응대로 고객의 시간을 절약하여 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cd22ec93-37e1-4bc6-8919-f086d4c78758\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0de290f9-df79-485e-af30-adb9dd5b1180\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-511d7ad7-4f7e-4859-b80f-d82fdb08a90f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223762600843/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1705ba77-571f-469a-88b9-3741c42be1d8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n<a class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223762600843/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f01847a9-c771-405a-806a-0792415bc0f1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5761a4c2-1492-4ba9-a677-d2c989cb4baa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c605fee-1983-4eac-8dc5-f1567edc6118\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">주문 수량에 대해 말씀드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-94192b87-498f-49ea-b4fb-8beeb3f6c55c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de030f0c-4729-442f-8cf1-6232bf07531b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수량은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-06622f13-7740-4166-abf1-517b714db296\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-46e09563-d608-4639-b31b-7c6da2ccd0a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플용으로는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1d8491fe-8cc9-4bca-8522-48144c2bd466\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0d817005-7e96-4d7c-9a38-1ae0348124f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>2개</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7ccc7b36-9c39-49d6-9af8-75a41c0622bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가 기본입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3c913658-696c-4aa4-a0e6-1a080644bae4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-096cc69b-3405-48c6-a0d8-0134a0758572\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-50de3235-d6c1-49e1-853d-5e8b720f5448\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-94ab0dcc-594d-47f1-8c72-7307b743e575\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플 아닌 소량 주문인 경우는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0ae327b5-512a-4649-91f0-80e177199aa8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7521c442-547f-4120-ab49-faa2e033ab81\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>50개</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f3a6aedf-fe7f-4f71-a4cf-eb7aa